filterEditorContextMenu

    filterEditorContextMenu(handler: FilterHandler<EditContextMenuFilterObject>): void

    Called just before the editor context menu is about to open. Allows adding items to it.

    desktop
    Parameters
        handler: FilterHandler<EditContextMenuFilterObject>

